1. *Minutu* sam čekao da se javiš na telefon. (I waited for *a minute* for you to answer the phone.)
2. Prošlo je *minutu* otkad si otišao. (It's been *a minute* since you left.)
3. Molim vas da pričekate *minutu*. (Please wait *a minute*.)
4. Sat otkucava poslednju *minutu* pred ponoć. (The clock is ticking the last *minute* before midnight.)
5. *Minutu* ti dajem da se skloniš odavde. (I'll give you *a minute* to get away from here.)
6. U poslednjoj *minuti* smo uspeli da postignemo gol. (We scored a goal in the last *minute*.)